column2: SELECT TOP #  s.subClass, g.oii_#_flux, oii_#_flux_err, oii_#_flux, oii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM GalSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObj AS s  ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid  WHERE  s.class = &&&  AND s.zwarning = #  AND (g.oii_#_flux & oii_#_flux & g.h_alpha_flux > #)
